{"tid":248911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"撒瑪利亞防止自殺會樓上 男子危坐天台企跳","createTime":"2017-05-19T02:36:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T03:52:32.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1420b9afb531d99b23dc3ee6c1d39c5f0f7ca9cc","tid":248911,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T02:36:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170519/large/1495159181_aab2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170519%2Flarge%2F1495159181_aab2.jpg&h=2e046663&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早上9時許，石硤尾白田邨瑞田樓一名中年男子，在天台危坐企圖跳樓。消防員接報到場游說，警方談判專家亦到場協助。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56713451&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170519\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56713451%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170519&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=bfcb1bda\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56713451%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170519&h=d59b0f6d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56713451&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170519</a>"},{"pid":"1e9c7c8502eceef4fd6f4116d1523900ca4ef879","tid":248911,"uid":53223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T02:37:04.000Z","msg":"唔洗打電話啦終於"},{"pid":"0326f6f74cb9fbd093303f22a6591f5438b794c3","tid":248911,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T02:37:44.000Z","msg":"即係剃人眼眉姐"},{"p